# 🐍 Snake Game (Python + Turtle)

A classic snake game built using Python's Turtle graphics module — created for fun and learning! 🎮✨

## 🚀 Features
- Snake movement and growth
- Score tracking with a scoreboard
- Collision detection
- Game over message

## 🎮 How to Run

1. Make sure Python 3 is installed.
2. Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/fatemepourseif/snake-game-python.git
